## Constraints

### Use

- **Turborepo** root `turbo.json` ile pipeline: `dev`, `build`, `test`, `lint`, `typecheck`
- **pnpm** 9+ (workspace catalog for shared versions)
- **TypeScript 5.x strict** — `packages/config/tsconfig/base.json` common + per-app override
- **ESLint 9** flat config + per-app override
- **Prettier 3** — single `.prettierrc` root
- **Vitest** test runner (Jest değil)
- **Node 20 LTS** — `.nvmrc` + package.json engines

### Avoid

- Lerna (Turborepo tek tool)
- npm / yarn (pnpm only)
- `@types/*` packages if TypeScript native types mevcutsa
- Global installs — her şey devDependencies
- Duplicate config across packages — shared `packages/config`

## Done Definition

- [ ] `pnpm install` at root — all workspaces resolved, no errors
- [ ] `pnpm -w run build` — all apps + packages build successfully
- [ ] `pnpm -w run lint` — green (empty projeler bile lint pass)
- [ ] `pnpm -w run typecheck` — green
- [ ] `pnpm -w run test` — green (empty test, ama tool çalışıyor)
- [ ] Turborepo cache çalışıyor (`pnpm -w run build` ikinci kez — cached)
- [ ] `.github/workflows/pr-check.yml` basic lint + typecheck + test job'ları
- [ ] README'de setup talimatları (`pnpm install`, `pnpm -w run dev`)
- [ ] `.env.example` her app için (boş değerli)
- [ ] Commit: `feat: monorepo scaffold with turborepo + pnpm workspaces`

## Explicit Don'ts

- Database kurma (Faz 2)
- Production Docker image (Faz 1 infra)
- Real code yazma — sadece scaffold
- CI/CD full setup — sadece basic pre-commit (Faz 9 infra)
- IaC (Terraform) — Faz 1

